{
  "texts": [
    "Retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) technology is a technique 14 that can enhance the accuracy of the response capabilities of LLMs by integrating local knowledge bases 15, 16.",
    "This technology has demonstrated significant potential in clinical applications 16.",
    "Therefore, the present study developed a local knowledge base focused on breast cancer to evaluate the application of RAG technology to the LLM for breast cancer nursing care question and answer (Q&A) systems.",
    "The overall performance of RAG-enhanced LLMs was evaluated, providing a theoretical foundation for their future application in clinical nursing practice and education.",
    "This study used GPT-4 (OpenAI) as the foundational model, as our research team has significant experience in using the ChatGPT-3.5 API."
  ]
}